1. Osećam *bolno* grlo već tri dana. (I feel *painful* throat for three days.)
2. Na dodir je mesto oko rane veoma *bolno*. (The area around the wound is very *sore* to the touch.)
3. Njegove reči su me *bolno* pogodile. (His words *painfully* affected me.)
4. Svi se slažemo da je ta situacija veoma *bolna*. (We all agree that the situation is very *painful*.)
5. Njena tuga bila je *bolna* za gledati. (Her grief was *painful* to watch.)
6. Tokom operacije osećala sam samo *bol*. (During the surgery, I only felt *pain*.)
7. Kada me je uhvatila grčevita bol, jedva sam disao. (When I was seized with *agonizing* pain, I could barely breathe.)
8. Ona je prošla kroz *bolne* tretmane kako bi se izborila sa bolešću. (She went through *painful* treatments to fight the illness.)